Package: VisiMod
Title: Model And Map Visibility Index Across Landscapes
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Katherine", "Mistick", , "katherinemistick@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A suite of tools for modeling visibility index using random
    forests.  Users provide a digital terrain (dtm) and digital surface
    (dsm) model and can generate models for omnidirectional (360ยบ) or
    user-defined directional visibility indexes.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
